## Understanding matricies: system of linear equations

Kelly's definition of multiplication lets us to write 
system of linear equations in matrix form:

 $$ \left\{ \begin{array}{ccccccc}
      a_{11} x_1 & + & \ldots & + & a_{1n} x_n & = & b_1 \\
                 & + & \ldots & + &            & = &     \\
      a_{m1} x_1 & + & \ldots & + & a_{mn} x_n & = & b_m \\
    \end{array} \right.
 $$

 $$ Ax = b $$

 How do we solve such systems?

